dataSource.query:
SELECT
	event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Days sales outstanding (days)",
    "Time to FI-AR item creation (days)",
    "Late Payments (%)",
    "Pymt. terms different in billing doc. & FI-AR (%)",
    "FI-AR items cleared without offered discount (%)",
    "Late Payments with discount (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AR items cleared")
        	AS "Days Sales outstanding (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - FI-AR items created") 
        	AS "Time to FI-AR item creation (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AR items cleared after net due date")*100
        	AS "Late Payments (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Payment terms different in billing document and FI-AR")*100 
			AS "Pymt. terms different in billing doc. & FI-AR (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AR items cleared without offered discount")*100
        	AS "FI-AR items cleared without offered discount (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - FI-AR items cleared after net due date but with discount applied") * 100 
        	AS "Late Payments with discount (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
